BECOME ELIGIBLE TO WIN $2500 WORTH OF HOOKER FURNITURE
On behalf of all the employees at Hooker Furniture Corporation, we thank you for purchasing our furniture. Your retailer can assist you in many areas. We would, however, like to know more about you. Therefore, we ask you to complete the following questionnaire. This will register your purchase, and you will become eligible for an annual drawing for $2500 (MSRP) worth of Hooker furniture through the dealer from whom you purchased this product. Please note that your responses will be used for our purposes only. No names will be sold to outside mailing companies.



