 stores, specialty retailers, department stores, catalog and internet merchants, interior designers and national and regional chains. Hooker Furniture was founded in 1924 and is headquartered in Martinsville, VA.    expand             Key People Hooker Furniture Corp.   Board of Directors    Name/Title Current Board Membership          Paul B. Toms, 60  Chairman & Chief Executive Officer   Hooker Furniture Corp.      Ellen Connelly Taaffe, 55  Independent Director   Hooker Furniture Corp.      John L. Gregory, 68  Independent Director   Young, Haskins, Mann, Gregory, Mcgarry & Wall PC, Hooker Furniture Corp.      David G. Sweet, 69  Independent Director   Hooker Furniture Corp.      Henry G. Williamson, 68  Independent Director   Williamson Corp., Williamson Media Corp., Hooker Furniture Corp., The Christian Community Foundation, Inc.      W. Christopher Beeler, 64  Lead Independent Director   Virginia Glass Products Corp., Virginia Mirror Co., Inc., Hooker Furniture Corp.      E. Larry Ryder, 66  Independent Director   Hooker Furniture Corp.       expand    All Executives     Paul B. Toms Chairman & Chief Executive Officer     Michael W. Delgatti President     George D. Revington Chief Operating Officer     Paul A. Huckfeldt CFO, SVP-Accounting & Head-Investor Relations     Anne M. Jacobsen Senior Vice President-Administration     Steve Lush President-Hooker Casegoods     Robert W. Sherwood Secretary, Treasurer & Vice President-Credit     Johne Albanese Vice President-Marketing     Raymond T. Harm Senior Vice President-Sales     Ellen Connelly Taaffe Independent Director     John L. Gregory Independent Director     David G. Sweet Independent Director     Henry G. Williamson Independent Director     W. Christopher Beeler Lead Independent Director     E. Larry Ryder Independent Director      expand         Advertisement            Average Growth Rates Hooker Furniture Corp.   Past Five Years Ending 01/31/2017 (Fiscal Year)     Revenue  +32.87%    Net Income  +38.71% 